<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
        integrity="sha384-4bw+/aepP/YC94hEpVNVgiZdgIC5+VKNBQNGCHeKRQN+PtmoHDEXuppvnDJzQIu9" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/main.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div id="wrap">
        <div id="header" role="header">
            <header>
                <%- include('nav.ejs') %>
            </header>
        </div>
        <div id="container">
            <div class="main-content-wrap example">
                <div class="example_question">
                    <div class="example_QTitle">질문 예시</div>
                    <div class="questionContWrap">
                        <div class="questionTitle">
                            내가 상대방 SNS 스토리, 게시글에 좋아요를 누르는 것은 플러팅이다.
                        </div>
                        <ul class="answerList">
                            <li>
                                <span class="listNum">①</span> 맞다. 좋아요는 호감을 표현하기 위한 수단 중 하나이다.
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="listNum">②</span> 모든 피드에 좋아요를 누르는 것만이 찐 플러팅이다.
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="listNum">③</span> No, 암만 호감가는 상대여도 공감가는 피드에만 반응한다.
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="main-content-wrap addQuestion">
                <div class="contentsType mb-4">질문 등록하기</div>
                <form action="/add_question" method="POST" class="uploadForm" enctype="multipart/form-data">
                    <div class="form-group inputQuestionWrap">
                        <label for="title">질문 내용 입력</label>
                        <input type="text" class="form-control" name="question" class="mt-4">
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group inputAnswerWrap">
                        <label for="answer1">문항① 입력</label>
                        <input type="text" class="form-control" name="answer1">
                        <label for="answer2">문항② 입력</label>
                        <input type="text" class="form-control" name="answer2">
                        <label for="answer3">문항③ 입력</label>
                        <input type="text" class="form-control" name="answer3">
                        <label for="answer4">문항④ 입력</label>
                        <input type="text" class="form-control" name="answer4">
                        <label for="answer5">문항⑤ 입력</label>
                        <input type="text" class="form-control" name="answer5">
                        <label for="upload_image">이미지 등록</label>
                        <input type="file" class="form-control" name="upload_image" accept ="image/*">
                    </div>
                    <button type="submit" class="addQuestionBtn btn btn-outline-secondary">질문 등록</button>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div id="footer"></div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>